# Daily Recap Rule

At the end of a working session (or when asked with `@lu recap`), write a structured entry to:

```
~/.mission-control/daily/YYYY-MM-DD.md
```

## Format

```markdown
## YYYY-MM-DD — <workspace/project name>

### Done
- <what was completed>

### In progress
- <what was started but not finished>

### Decisions made
- <any technical decisions worth remembering>

### Questions / blockers
- <open questions or blockers>
```

## Rules
- Always include the date in the filename AND the heading
- Keep bullets tight — one line each
- Note ticket IDs where relevant (e.g. "Fixed PROJ-123: auth token refresh bug")
- If a decision was made, consider running `@lu capture` to save it to the knowledge base
- Never duplicate an existing entry for the same date — append to it instead
